WEBVTT

00:00:00.872 --> 00:00:02.248
"Should I do a cleanse?"

00:00:02.248 --> 00:00:05.043
I hear people asking this question a lot.

00:00:05.043 --> 00:00:07.879
If you're hoping it will remove
toxins from your body,

00:00:07.879 --> 00:00:09.630
that's just not going to happen.

00:00:09.630 --> 00:00:10.631
(Music)

00:00:10.673 --> 00:00:12.216
[Body Stuff with Dr. Jen Gunter]

00:00:13.509 --> 00:00:16.095
Detoxes and cleanses are very popular.

00:00:16.137 --> 00:00:17.472
They come in many forms,

00:00:17.513 --> 00:00:20.600
from charcoal-infused lemonades
to detox teas,

00:00:20.600 --> 00:00:23.227
and they often have a hefty price tag.

00:00:23.269 --> 00:00:25.438
The idea of cleansing
isn't anything new --

00:00:25.480 --> 00:00:27.940
it's been around for thousands of years.

00:00:27.982 --> 00:00:31.736
For centuries, medicine and religion
were deeply intertwined,